$ON_SRCRET
Onevent BEFORE_INPUT Call AS_SRCRET(zc) From W1HRMAT3
Onevent CONTROL Call C_SRCRET(zc) From W1HRMAT3
Onevent AFTER_CHANGE Gosub AMM_SRCRET From W1HRMAT3
Return

Subprog AS_SRCRET(VALEUR)
Variable Char    VALEUR()
Local Integer INDIC : INDIC = indice
Raz mkstat
Call TEXTE(46714,GBOUT1) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(6028,GBOUTS) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(12276,GBOUTP) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(16134,GBOUTA) From OBJDIV
## Action STD
Call AS_SRCRET(VALEUR) From SUBEML2
If mkstat=2
 [M]SRCRET(INDIC) = VALEUR
 Affzo SRCRET(INDIC) : mkstat = 2
Endif
Onkey 129 Titled GBOUT1 Call B1_SRCRET(zc) From W1HRMAT3
Onkey   2 Titled GBOUTS Call S_SRCRET(zc) From W1HRMAT3
Onkey 144 Titled GBOUTP Call P_SRCRET(zc) From W1HRMAT3
Onkey 146 Titled GBOUTA Call SA_SRCRET(zc) From W1HRMAT3
Gosub _AFF
End

Subprog C_SRCRET(VALEUR)
Variable Char    VALEUR()
## Action %CNTOBJ
Call CONTSEL("GRI","!",VALEUR,"",mkstat) From CONTOBJ
If mkstat : GERR = 1 : GZONE = "SRCRET" : GZNUM = 14077 : Endif
Gosub _AFF
End

